{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/2019/05/17/README","result":{"data":{"content":{"edges":[{"node":{"id":"fdaae571-02eb-572a-bf45-6730bd848987","html":"<h2 id=\"calpa-的技術博客-starter\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#calpa-%E7%9A%84%E6%8A%80%E8%A1%93%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2-starter\" aria-label=\"calpa 的技術博客 starter permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Calpa 的技術博客 Starter</h2>\n<p>透過這個 Starter，你可以快速建立一個如同 <a href=\"https://calpa.me\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Calpa's Blog</a> 的博客系統。</p>\n<h2 id=\"功能\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD\" aria-label=\"功能 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>功能</h2>\n<h3 id=\"系統架構\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E7%B3%BB%E7%B5%B1%E6%9E%B6%E6%A7%8B\" aria-label=\"系統架構 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>系統架構</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>GatsbyJS v2，更加快速</li>\n<li>Google Analytics</li>\n<li>支持離線操作</li>\n<li>Web App Manifest</li>\n<li>Netlify 網站優化</li>\n<li>精美評論區 (powered by <a href=\"https://github.com/gitalk/gitalk\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Gitalk</a>)</li>\n<li>高速解析 Markdown (基於<a href=\"https://www.gatsbyjs.org/packages/gatsby-transformer-remark/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">gatsby-transformer-remark</a>)</li>\n<li>支持站點地圖</li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"設計\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E8%A8%AD%E8%A8%88\" aria-label=\"設計 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>設計</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>分頁設計</li>\n<li>響應式設計</li>\n<li>自動加載 Font Awesome (基於 <a href=\"https://github.com/FortAwesome/react-fontawesome\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">react-fontawesome</a>)</li>\n<li>流暢滑動設計 (基於 <a href=\"https://github.com/cferdinandi/smooth-scroll\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">smooth-scroll</a>)</li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"數據來源\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E6%95%B8%E6%93%9A%E4%BE%86%E6%BA%90\" aria-label=\"數據來源 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>數據來源</h3>\n<p>你可以直接修改 <code class=\"language-text\">/src/content/*.md</code>，或者是使用 <a href=\"https://www.netlifycms.org\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Netlify-cms</a> 來編輯文章。</p>\n<h3 id=\"可自定的地方\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%8F%AF%E8%87%AA%E5%AE%9A%E7%9A%84%E5%9C%B0%E6%96%B9\" aria-label=\"可自定的地方 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>可自定的地方</h3>\n<p>如果你覺得這個系統需要更加完善的話，你可以從下面的地方入手：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>搜索引擎優化</li>\n<li>使用 SCSS 來自定義樣式</li>\n<li>數據來源</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"快速入門\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%BF%AB%E9%80%9F%E5%85%A5%E9%96%80\" aria-label=\"快速入門 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>快速入門</h2>\n<h3 id=\"使用-netlify-部署\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8-netlify-%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2\" aria-label=\"使用 netlify 部署 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>使用 Netlify 部署</h3>\n<p>你可以使用以下按鈕來構建和部署博客的一個副本：</p>\n<p>在你點擊上面的按鈕之後，你就會賦予 Netlify 取得你的 Github 授權，以及選擇倉庫名稱。Netlify 會自動創建一個倉庫，並且複製那裡的文件。</p>\n<p>之後，它會自動構建和部署一個新的網站，為你帶來一個完整的博客系統。</p>\n<h3 id=\"使用-codesandbox-來寫代碼\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8-codesandbox-%E4%BE%86%E5%AF%AB%E4%BB%A3%E7%A2%BC\" aria-label=\"使用 codesandbox 來寫代碼 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>使用 Codesandbox 來寫代碼</h3>\n<p>你可以使用以下按鈕來嘗試修改博客系統的代碼：</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://codesandbox.io/s/github/calpa/gatsby-starter-calpa-blog/tree/master/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://codesandbox.io/static/img/play-codesandbox.svg\" alt=\"Edit blog\"></a></p>\n<p>如果你喜歡 <a href=\"https://calpa.me\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">我的博客</a>，請給個 star，多謝。</p>\n<h2 id=\"前提\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%89%8D%E6%8F%90\" aria-label=\"前提 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>前提</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Git</li>\n<li>Node：從 8.5.0 或更高版本開始的任何 8.x 版本</li>\n<li>fork 本項目 （想要貢獻的話）</li>\n<li>在本地計算機上克隆本項目</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"開發\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E9%96%8B%E7%99%BC\" aria-label=\"開發 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>開發</h2>\n<p>如何運行?</p>\n<ol>\n<li>安裝 Gatsby-CLI</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-text line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-text\">npm install --global gatsby-cli</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>使用 Gatsby 啟動器創建新的 Gatsby 項目，<code class=\"language-text\">awesome-blog</code>是您博客的文件夾</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-text line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-text\">gatsby new awesome-blog https://github.com/calpa/gatsby-starter-calpa-blog</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>打開文件夾</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-text line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-text\">cd awesome-blog</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<ol start=\"4\">\n<li>\n<p>運行開發服務器</p>\n<ol>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">npm start</code> 啟動熱重載開發服務器 (基於<a href=\"https://www.gatsbyjs.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Gatsby</a>)</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">open http://localhost:8000</code> 在您喜歡的瀏覽器中打開</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"配置\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE\" aria-label=\"配置 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>配置</h2>\n<p>在 <code class=\"language-text\">data/config</code>編輯 exports 的對象</p>\n<p>註意壹下: <a href=\"https://www.colorhexa.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">想要查找 theme_color 十六進制代碼，請單擊此處。</a></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-javascript line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">module<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>exports <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  title<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'your blog title here'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  maxPages<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">12</span>\n  meta<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    description<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'blog description'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    keyword<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'blog, JavaScript'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    theme_color<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'#hexcode'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    favicon<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'https:yourimageurl.com'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    google_site_verification<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'your google verification hash'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  name<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'your name'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  email<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'your_email@gmail.com'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  iconUrl<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'https://youricon.jpg'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  License<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'by'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  url<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'https://yourblog.me'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  about<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'/2018/05/01/about-your-name/'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// Sidebar</span>\n  zhihuUsername<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'your zhiu user name here'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  githubUsername<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'your github user name here'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  friends<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      title<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'friend title'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      href<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'link to their blog'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>插件的配置文件:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-javascript line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">gaOptimizeId<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'GTM-WHP7SC5'</span><s